name: Voyage
description: Early edition from the series 'Dark Realities' by trnvirsingh. Voyage is the last artwork from the Sci-Fi theme in the series. Inspired from the early 60s sci-fi films, tt illustrate the end point of the long journey for humans to finally reach at the start of new exploration. It is prequel artwork of 'Substantial snag' which further lead to 'The last probe'
